def_en: Something that is untouched by something else is not affected by it.

def_cn: 完好无缺的；未受损害的
def_en: If something is untouched, it is not damaged in any way, although it has been in a situation where it could easily have been damaged.

def_cn: 世外桃源般的；不染尘嚣的；天然质朴的
def_en: An untouched area or place is thought to be beautiful because it is still in its original state and has not been changed or damaged in any way.

def_cn: 未吃过（或喝过）的；未动过的
def_en: If food or drink is untouched, none of it has been eaten or drunk.
